{"tid":2422332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【自由時報】向華強父子申請來台居留 移民署：依法駁回","createTime":"2021-02-25T06:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T10:39:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"28ce6b2c1c48797ea5500ccc30ed4a18f2c99c43","tid":2422332,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"賭神系列電影中飾演「龍五」而聞名的香港影視大亨向華強，日前與兒子向佐向我政府申請來台依親居留；不過，向佐具有中共黨政軍背景，向華強也曾擔任中國電影基金會名譽副會長，與中共官方關係匪淺。移民署、國安局和陸委會等機關召開聯審會議後，駁回其申請。<br />\n<br />\n移民署指出，有關香港向氏父子申請在台居留案，經會商相關單位審查，認有「香港澳門居民進入台灣地區及居留定居許可辦法」第22條所規定之不予許可情形，因此依規定不予許可居留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3449152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3449152&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=6d2f0823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3449152&h=a73d08c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3449152</a>"},{"pid":"79766376a7f02717e11fd1af6096aae0ddc6d200","tid":2422332,"uid":3177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:23:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">想走？</span>"},{"pid":"fc76c5bd10f5414693d2f3365ed119612f767d92","tid":2422332,"uid":80332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760b95d1be0f65f71c3f471da89d26e29794685b","tid":2422332,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8e50218e43a4661e1d72ed97316b74d2ab127a","tid":2422332,"uid":174502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:26:38.000Z","msg":"點解要去台灣做二等公民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji